div.div: Light Yagami is a genius high school student who is about to learn about life through a book of death. When a bored shinigami, a God of Death, named Ryuk drops a black notepad called a Death Note, Light receives power over life and death with the stroke of a pen. Determined to use this dark gift for the best, Light sets out to rid the world of evil namely, the people he believes to be evil. Should anyone hold such power? The consequences of Lights actions will set the world ablaze. (Source: Viz Media)

An AI named Matsumoto appears before Vivy, the worlds first autonomous humanoid AI. Matsumotos mission is to rewrite history together with Vivy, in order to stop the war between AI and humans that will happen one century later.
(Source: Funimation)
